race.comment: NEW SURPRISE (7) turned in a plain performance last time when fifth at this track over 401m behind Catch Me Diva (23.44) in a Grade 5. Can atone. ZIPPING ZEYATTA (1) was safely held last time out, finishing seventh at this track over 520m behind Zipping Admiral (30.47) in a Grade 5. Placed at her previous run. Still to record a win from this draw but has never missed the frame in two starts. Must be included in calculations. GLOBAL TRACKER (2) doesn't have the best strike-rate but recent form is sound. Has finished in the money at the last three runs. Likely to be in the finish again. ZIG ZAG ZOEY (8) must be included in calculations.
